 Season Four preview Trailer

Hey guy's here is a link to a Season Four preview I made on my pc round about the time Season Four had just finished:
Season Four General Preview

Some pointers:

1. I had a crappy sound card so I could not record the voice from video. So all the voices in the trailer had to be downloaded from P3X595 and lip synced with the mouths. So on some clips the words are slightly out of sync with what is being said, but its not too bad.

2. All the sounds were downloaded or retrieved from other sourses. EG. There is a shot of the sun blowing up. Listen carefully and you'll notice that sound effect used is that of The Pyramid ship being Nuked and Ra Screaming from the original movie

3. A bit that I particularly like is the part where Sam says, "This is the Sun orbiting Vorash" and we then cut to the jacob saying "We wanna blow it up" and then we cut to a shot of the sun blowing up. I made that edit way before season five started. When I watched the 1st eppy of Season five they had a "previously on" and they used the exact same edit. Sam saying those exact same words, cutting to her dad saying the same words and the cutting to a shot of the sun blowing up. The only difference with mine is the sound effect (see previous point). So when I saw the episode with the previously on I was like "Oh yeah!"

4. You'll need quicktime on your PC to view the file www.apple.com/quicktime
Quicktime is the best movie compressor on the net when it comes to short trailers and the like(IMHO). All you who have trailers downloaded on ur pc shood be able to see it as they are all compressed in quicktime.

5. The file is 1.95 mb in size.

6. The trailer aint very well structured. I just through together a few cool shots here and there, a few funny lines, on top of some music by Craig Armstrong (Escape) and voila. I make a better attempt at the S5 trailer I will. I'll look more into the story arc of Anubis. I had just downloaded the track "Escape" and so I wanted to make a cool S4 preview using it.

7. Enjoy!
